At the [[2020 United States Census|2020 census]] there were 207 people, 59 households, and 43 families living in the CDP.  The population density was 37 people per square mile. There were 82 housing units.

The median household income was $22,106. The per capita income for the CDP was $11,430.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arizona.hometownlocator.com/az/pima/san-miguel.cfm |publisher=Arizona.hometownlocator.com |access-date=2021-08-25 |date=2021 |title=San Simon, AZ Profile: Facts & Data}}</ref>

